dfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=f1ffc61e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n二、輿論戰線：<br />\n香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；<br />\n香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：<br />\n【我們香港人】倡導計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=0fa1096a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"92983fa668479d5d25842a0075df36d891bc53f3","tid":1679820,"uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"老納隻狗"},{"pid":"25e48b0f7a87ebd904e0b0a10eb76c66cb1dfa78","tid":1679820,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"休班警"},{"pid":"1352266d4686d793b278b916b2496e607ed6fcea","tid":1679820,"uid":322388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"屌你 影片圖 又fake咗我㩒"},{"pid":"af770aaa90046e974cf964f5998508141e7bbdc3","tid":1679820,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma